W-Building-Repair — DONE 2026-05-02

Architect 2026-05-02: "If the player hovers next to the building for 3 seconds,
repair starts which drains wood." Mirrors the constructionTick proximity-drain
pattern as additive behavior — does not change the build flow.

## Tunables (NAMED — Architect monetization hook for future ad-buff "repair 2× speed")

- REPAIR_HOVER_DELAY  = 3.0 s   (player must stand near before repair starts)
- REPAIR_RATE         = 0.25 s  (per wood consumed)
- REPAIR_HP_PER_WOOD  = 8       (HP restored per wood)
- REPAIR_RANGE        = 36      (world units — proximity threshold, just past CONSTRUCT_RADIUS=28)

Exposed on `WG.HuntPlayer.REPAIR_TUNABLES` (frozen) for hunt-render.

